## Testing Philosophy

### Test Pyramid

```
        /\
       /  \      Few, slow, expensive
      / UI \     System/Integration Tests
     /------\
    /        \   
   / Service  \  More, medium speed
  /------------\ 
 /              \
/  Unit Tests    \ Many, fast, cheap
------------------
```

**Distribution:**
- **70%** Unit tests (models, helpers, services)
- **20%** Integration tests (controllers, requests)
- **10%** System tests (full user flows)

